Dialogue: 0,0:00:01.03,0:00:02.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:02.37,0:00:05.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That guest is, make me please pin badge.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:05.32,0:00:07.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The same as one you brought.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:07.94,0:00:10.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He's the one who asked you \Nto make the pin badge, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:14.04,0:00:15.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What kind of man was he?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:16.12,0:00:17.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What kind?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:17.63,0:00:19.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hmm...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:19.94,0:00:21.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Like a barrel.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:21.18,0:00:22.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Who?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:22.44,0:00:23.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Barrel Titor?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:23.89,0:00:25.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Titor?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:25.02,0:00:27.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No, no. Just like barrel.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:28.54,0:00:30.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Just like barrel...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:30.23,0:00:32.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The Japanese word for barrel is "taru"!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:32.98,0:00:33.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Taru?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:34.90,0:00:38.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,A while back, it was in a Rai-Net anime.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:38.06,0:00:40.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There was this barrel-like monster...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:40.74,0:00:41.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:41.60,0:00:43.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Just a taru.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:43.55,0:00:44.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Or balloon.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:44.52,0:00:48.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,A man like a barrel or a balloon?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:48.28,0:00:50.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Where can we contact him?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:50.20,0:00:51.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:51.51,0:00:53.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Private information.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:53.21,0:00:54.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Nothing.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:58.50,0:01:00.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No clues, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:00.78,0:01:03.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But if the man's pin badge is finished,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:03.53,0:01:04.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,won't he pick it up?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:04.78,0:01:07.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He told the man it would take a week to make,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:07.29,0:01:09.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,so he left without placing the order.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:09.16,0:01:10.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:10.77,0:01:13.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So we have to give up?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:13.91,0:01:14.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:16.09,0:01:17.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There's still one way.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:19.14,0:01:21.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}If I wait for the time leap machine's completion tomorrow,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:21.99,0:01:23.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}and go back in time...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.08,0:03:02.06,Title1,,0000,0000,0000,,Sacrificial Necrosis
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.40,0:03:04.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Where's Suzuha?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.66,0:03:07.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Didn't she just leave?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.34,0:03:08.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why are you asking?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.52,0:03:09.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll explain later!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.95,0:03:14.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Damn.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.38,0:03:17.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I forgot to ask when the man was coming.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.60,0:03:19.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, welcome.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.73,0:03:20.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Is that him?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.38,0:03:25.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}He was right. The silhouette is \Nlike a barrel or a balloon.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.68,0:03:29.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Daru?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.58,0:03:32.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Okarin...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.42,0:03:35.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Jeez.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.26,0:03:38.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why did you decide to get a fake pin badge?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.04,0:03:42.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wouldn't it suck if she couldn't find her dad?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.32,0:03:44.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So I figured I'd show her the badge
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.82,0:03:47.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,and make a fake Titor.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.35,0:03:49.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So you wanted to get her excited over nothing?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.70,0:03:52.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There are two types of lies.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.64,0:03:55.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Lies that hurt, and lies that don't—
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.27,0:03:59.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Do you really think Suzuha would want that?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.69,0:04:09.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Miss Amane told me not to tell anyone this, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.91,0:04:15.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That time machine can only travel backward.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.43,0:04:21.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Once you go, you can't return.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.93,0:04:26.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,How's it going?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.57,0:04:28.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Something to drink.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.59,0:04:34.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, you brought me an ice-cold zero-calorie cola!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.45,0:04:36.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're too kind.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.03,0:04:37.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Well?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.87,0:04:39.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Can we fix the time machine?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.06,0:04:40.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Probably by tomorrow.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.77,0:04:43.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Even working this whole time, \Nthat's still amazing!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.52,0:04:45.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Daru's the real thing.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.86,0:04:47.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I told you not to judge him by his looks.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.52,0:04:50.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Did you say that?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.15,0:04:55.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Even if he looks unhealthy and kind of dim...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.58,0:04:57.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah. I've changed my mind about him.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.68,0:05:00.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Then you help me, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.10,0:05:02.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And then, in the steaming hot confines \Nof the time machine,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.18,0:05:05.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,we can forget our shame \Nand take off our clothes...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.92,0:05:07.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Shut up, pervert!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.46,0:05:11.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Daru-kun and Suzu-san look good together.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.76,0:05:17.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, I'm saying this because
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.95,0:05:21.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't think I'll ever have \Nthe chance to say it again.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.60,0:05:25.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm really grateful to you all.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.56,0:05:29.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,When I first came here, I didn't know anyone.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.37,0:05:33.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Even though this era is much more peaceful,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.22,0:05:36.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,somehow, to me, it was really scary.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.29,0:05:40.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But now I have lots of friends.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.31,0:05:42.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm really happy that I could come here...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.29,0:05:45.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That I could spend time with you guys.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.59,0:05:47.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I really had fun.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.39,0:05:52.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm glad I could be a lab member,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.14,0:05:54.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,just for a while.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.20,0:05:56.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm glad I could spend time with you...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.62,0:06:00.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Once you go, you can't return.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.02,0:06:02.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Okabe Rintarou!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.45,0:06:03.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Change the future—
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.21,0:06:05.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll make sure to change the future!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.72,0:06:09.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll make it a free world, like this one!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.92,0:06:12.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Okabe Rintarou?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.33,0:06:13.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Do you...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.65,0:06:17.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Do you regret the memories you've made?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.29,0:06:22.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Having to say goodbye, do you think that
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.21,0:06:25.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,it would have been better if we'd all never met?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.53,0:06:28.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Do you regret it?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.66,0:06:32.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hashida Itaru told you?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.36,0:06:35.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He's worried about you, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.18,0:06:37.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm going!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.55,0:06:40.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Changing the future was my father's wish...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.40,0:06:44.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And you don't care what will happen to you?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.13,0:06:47.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The '70s weren't a bad time.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.80,0:06:54.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll make friends like you there, \Nand I'll live freely.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.00,0:07:04.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Okay, here goes.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.42,0:07:13.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I think it's fine, but give it a final check.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.70,0:07:19.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It looks like it works.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.98,0:07:21.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You really are amazing!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.64,0:07:24.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You should be happier...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.48,0:07:27.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You just fixed a time machine.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.34,0:07:29.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,1975...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.39,0:07:31.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I wonder what month and day I should go to.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.46,0:07:33.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What's good for this? Taiankichijitsu?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.87,0:07:35.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Or Tomobiki?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.09,0:07:36.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Those days are for weddings.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.80,0:07:38.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But Tomobiki might be good.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.85,0:07:41.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It could help you make new friends faster.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.81,0:07:44.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Friends? That would be nice.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.12,0:07:50.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,FG204?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.25,0:07:52.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, Suzu-san?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.32,0:07:54.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.68,0:07:55.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What's this?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.75,0:08:00.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's what my dad named the time machine.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.67,0:08:09.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,M-My bike?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.90,0:08:12.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I thought it might fit
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.21,0:08:14.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,if we removed the tires.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.21,0:08:15.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You really like it, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.32,0:08:19.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.16,0:08:20.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll take care of it.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.97,0:08:22.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Thanks.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.67,0:08:24.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I got it!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.70,0:08:29.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Mayushii figured out who your dad is!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.81,0:08:32.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.91,0:08:36.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And they're right nearby!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.17,0:08:39.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wh-Where?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.03,0:08:41.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I've always felt
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.55,0:08:44.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,that you two make a good pair.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.62,0:08:47.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But I understand now.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.63,0:08:51.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's because you're father and daughter.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.23,0:08:52.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Y-You can't mean...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.45,0:08:55.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Suzu-san's dad is...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.40,0:08:57.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Daru-kun!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.06,0:09:02.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.06,0:09:04.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's not funny!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.45,0:09:06.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The idea of this pervert getting married...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.49,0:09:08.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey! Isn't that a little mean?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.73,0:09:10.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Please explain.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.24,0:09:12.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,How did you come to this conclusion?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.65,0:09:16.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,First, "barrel" means "taru," right?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.10,0:09:19.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Taru... Daru... Daru-kun?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.31,0:09:20.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,A pun?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.60,0:09:22.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's a reason?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.32,0:09:24.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But Okarin and Barrel Titor
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.84,0:09:29.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,were also part of the group that helped \Nfound the resistance, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.02,0:09:35.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And in 2010, Akihabara, \Nthey were working on a time machine.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.16,0:09:37.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And they knew about Okarin's Reading Signer...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.41,0:09:39.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Reading Steiner.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.07,0:09:41.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,They knew about it.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.33,0:09:43.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That only leaves Daru-kun.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.93,0:09:48.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And then, the most convincing proof \NMayushii found was...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.13,0:09:52.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The name of the time machine?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.15,0:09:53.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,FG204.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.72,0:09:55.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's a future gadget.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.36,0:09:57.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,A future gadget?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.67,0:10:01.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And there's stuff to the right of it, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.77,0:10:05.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,"Future Gadget 204,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.10,0:10:07.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,2nd Edition, Ver. 2.31"!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.10,0:10:11.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That naming convention...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.87,0:10:21.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Dad...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.46,0:10:27.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Y-You should say, "Papa!" at a time like this.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.05,0:10:28.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't be a pervert right now!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.92,0:10:37.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Dad.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.03,0:10:40.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Y-Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.23,0:10:43.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm here...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.10,0:10:44.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I came to see you...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.87,0:10:48.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...in the time machine you made.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.81,0:10:55.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll do what you attempted,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.35,0:10:57.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,so watch me.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.02,0:11:00.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, I'm watching.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.10,0:11:02.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll always be watching.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.40,0:11:13.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,By the way...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.88,0:11:15.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Was your mom cute?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.47,0:11:19.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I want a short one, with a baby face and big boobs.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.48,0:11:25.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll keep that a secret.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.77,0:11:30.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Then, I'll be going.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.73,0:11:35.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't forget about Mayushii and the rest of us!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.09,0:11:35.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Be careful.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.39,0:11:37.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll be fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.99,0:11:41.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll find IBN 5100.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.41,0:11:43.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And I'll get it for you.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.49,0:11:47.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So please, change the future.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.49,0:11:52.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll see you in thirty-five years.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.57,0:11:55.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I guess it'll only be a few hours for you.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.18,0:12:01.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Suzu-san!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.62,0:12:18.10,CellphoneR,,0000,0000,0000,,From: Part-Time Warrior \NSubject: Thank You \N\NGoodbye.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.87,0:12:24.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Suzuha!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.42,0:12:26.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's be sure we see each other again!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.92,0:12:29.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll keep working hard until then.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.52,0:12:31.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So you try, too!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.38,0:12:42.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Good luck...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.26,0:12:47.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We've received word
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.32,0:12:49.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,that the satellite that fell
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.18,0:12:51.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,on the Akihabara Radio Building has vanished.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.91,0:12:57.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, do you think this pin badge \Ncould be our initials?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.70,0:12:58.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Okabe's "O."
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.74,0:12:59.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hashida's "H."
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.80,0:13:00.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Shiina's "S."
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.86,0:13:05.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Then "M" is Makise. And "A" is Amane, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.89,0:13:07.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,A lab member badge, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.63,0:13:09.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You want to make one?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.30,0:13:10.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's a good idea.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.38,0:13:12.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What's wrong, Okabe?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.83,0:13:16.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The Divergence Meter hasn't changed.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.50,0:13:21.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Will it change after Amane brings us \Nthe IBN 5100 or something?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.38,0:13:26.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Suzuha's fifty-four now.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.76,0:13:30.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,My daughter's over thirty years older than I am...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.82,0:13:33.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,She might be married, with grandkids.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.30,0:13:39.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,S-So at this age, I could see \Nmy own great-grandkids?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.05,0:13:42.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You should act really grown-up, \Nlike a great-grandfather!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.85,0:13:44.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,She's here!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.77,0:13:58.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Mr. Braun?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.50,0:14:03.77,Sign16A,,0000,0000,0000,,Okabe \NRintarou
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.77,0:14:04.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,A letter?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.75,0:14:07.02,Sign16A,,0000,0000,0000,,Hashida \NSuzu
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.54,0:14:08.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hashida Suzu?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.82,0:14:10.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Is that from Suzu-san?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.41,0:14:11.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Seriously?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.33,0:14:13.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why do you have that?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.11,0:14:16.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's a letter from someone \Nwho once took care of me.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.66,0:14:20.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,She asked me to give it to you today.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.36,0:14:22.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Where is she now?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.54,0:14:23.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,She died.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.18,0:14:29.18,Sign16A,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(1,889)}Hashida \NSuzu
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.49,0:14:27.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ten years ago.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.58,0:14:33.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Okabe Rintarou-sama...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.36,0:14:34.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}It's been so long.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.73,0:14:35.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}It's me, Amane Suzuha.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.79,0:14:39.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}It may have only been a few hours to you,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.07,0:14:43.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}but right now, it's June 13th, 2000.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.83,0:14:46.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I'll get straight to the point.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.85,0:14:48.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I failed.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.09,0:14:54.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I failed. I failed. I failed.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.32,0:14:58.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I failed. I failed. I failed.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.23,0:15:02.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I failed. I failed. I have failed.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.14,0:15:05.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I failed. I failed. I failed.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.55,0:15:11.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I only remembered who I was a year ago.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.90,0:15:15.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}For the past twenty-four years, I'd forgotten myself.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.26,0:15:18.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}The time travel didn't work right.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.28,0:15:21.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}The repair job was imperfect.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:22.39,0:15:24.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}But it wasn't my dad's fault.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.80,0:15:27.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}It was mine!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.60,0:15:31.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I should have gone directly to 1975.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.86,0:15:34.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I shouldn't have stopped in 2010.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.91,0:15:37.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I shouldn't have been so selfish.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.40,0:15:39.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Now, the future won't change!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.76,0:15:44.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I couldn't get an IBN 5100.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.10,0:15:48.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I'm sorry...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.10,0:15:50.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I'm so sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.33,0:15:58.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Why have I even lived this long?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.10,0:16:02.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I forgot my duty and spent my life doing nothing.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.81,0:16:06.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Forgive me! Forgive me! Forgive me! Forgive me!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.93,0:16:07.93,CellphoneL,,0000,0000,0000,,Part-Time Warrior \NThank You \N\NGoodbye.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.10,0:16:11.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Okabe Rintarou, when I tried to go to 1975,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.38,0:16:14.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}after the time machine forum meeting, \Nyou stopped me.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.64,0:16:21.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Because of the rain that night, \Nthe time machine broke.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.68,0:16:24.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}If you can go back in time,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.99,0:16:27.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I ask that you not stop me back then.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.11,0:16:31.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}My life...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.15,0:16:33.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}...was wasted.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.56,0:16:46.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Mr. Braun.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.31,0:16:48.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What's wrong?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.43,0:16:50.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You look down.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.41,0:16:55.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Please tell me how Hashida Suzu-san died.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.87,0:16:58.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What do you care?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.92,0:17:01.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I have to know how she died!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.46,0:17:04.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No matter how it was,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.65,0:17:07.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I have to know!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.84,0:17:12.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This doesn't seem like simple curiosity.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.70,0:17:16.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But what's your relationship to Suzu-san, anyway?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.39,0:17:18.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,A long-ago acquaintance...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.04,0:17:20.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Very long ago.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.33,0:17:23.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But I still remember
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.63,0:17:25.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,our time together well.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.75,0:17:30.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I really don't want to say it...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.41,0:17:31.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It was suicide.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.47,0:17:34.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,She hanged herself in her home.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.63,0:17:38.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,For about a year before she died,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.85,0:17:41.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,she was mentally unstable.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.18,0:17:48.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But up until then,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.10,0:17:50.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,she was a cheerful, kind person.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:01.77,0:18:03.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's all my fault...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.47,0:18:07.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The time machine broke because
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.03,0:18:09.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I stopped her back then.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.84,0:18:12.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If I'd never sent that D-mail,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:12.12,0:18:15.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,she'd have gone to 1975 then!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.05,0:18:17.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Okarin...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.35,0:18:21.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, Okabe, what are you doing?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:22.33,0:18:25.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}At this rate, Mayuri's going to...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:28.15,0:18:30.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Okarin, are you sending a D-mail?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.75,0:18:35.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If you do that, all of this will disappear!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.00,0:18:36.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I know that...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:36.66,0:18:38.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,All the time we remember spending
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.58,0:18:40.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,with Suzu-san won't have happened.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:40.52,0:18:41.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I know that!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:41.77,0:18:44.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}So please, change the future.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.47,0:18:48.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Okarin!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.08,0:19:01.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What is it, Okabe?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.10,0:19:07.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hashida Suzu?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:07.00,0:19:09.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I haven't heard that name in a long time.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:09.00,0:19:11.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Did you know her?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.45,0:19:12.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:12.68,0:19:15.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Um, is she still...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.32,0:19:18.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I guess it's been ten years...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:18.43,0:19:21.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,She really looked after me for a while.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:21.28,0:19:24.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I would've liked to have seen her at the end.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:25.14,0:19:27.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Did she commit suicide?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:28.14,0:19:30.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,She died of an illness!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.27,0:19:34.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I live in her house.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.82,0:19:38.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That bike...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:38.93,0:19:43.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, she always really loved it.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:43.81,0:19:45.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I couldn't throw it out.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:45.30,0:19:48.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So for ten years, I've kept it.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.88,0:19:53.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,At first, she and I were neighbors.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.98,0:19:55.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And then, one day,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:55.48,0:19:58.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,my house burned down in a fire.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:58.21,0:20:00.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I lost everything.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:00.09,0:20:03.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And she let me stay here.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:03.04,0:20:05.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Was she alone that whole time?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:06.31,0:20:08.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,She never married...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:08.87,0:20:11.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,She was a little strange.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:12.11,0:20:13.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Once, I asked her
Dialogue: 0,0:20:13.84,0:20:17.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,why she'd done all this for someone \Nwith no relationship to her.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:17.51,0:20:20.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And then she laughed, and she said this...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:21.08,0:20:22.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,"Everyone gets help
Dialogue: 0,0:20:22.57,0:20:25.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,from someone else, at some point in their lives.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:25.33,0:20:29.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So someday, you should help someone, too."
Dialogue: 0,0:20:30.68,0:20:31.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, that's right.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:31.85,0:20:32.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,One second...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:34.18,0:20:36.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Suzu-san had this.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:37.28,0:20:39.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Do you know what the number means?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:41.31,0:20:45.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,She was always looking at it, \Nfrom her hospital bed.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:45.21,0:20:49.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Is this the number before it changes? Or after?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:49.18,0:20:51.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Did I manage to change it?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:51.37,0:20:54.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Whatever it was, it bothered her to the end.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:58.72,0:21:01.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}The divergence number changed.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:02.87,0:21:05.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}But it hasn't gone beyond 1%.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:06.28,0:21:09.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The train for the outer line will arrive shortly.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:09.81,0:21:12.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Please stand behind the yellow line.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:11.27,0:21:14.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}The Yamanote Line is working at this time?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:14.56,0:21:15.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Mayuri!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:20.54,0:21:21.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Damn it.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:28.69,0:21:29.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Mayuri!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:39.80,0:21:41.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What's wrong, Okarin?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:41.87,0:21:43.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's nothing.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:44.36,0:21:49.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, Mayushii's phone rang. Was that you?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:49.72,0:21:52.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,She was having a nice nap, so I didn't wake her.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:59.22,0:22:03.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Suzuha... Did the world change?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:04.41,0:22:08.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Has Mayuri been saved?
